        :ElseIf d<ld
            stk←(1+0.5×ld-d)↓stk
            stk,⍨←⊂f
        :Else
            ⍝59  #.Conga.LIB.Send                          4     377       7.371103391051292          35.96187336370349         1131      3770
            ⍝60  #.Conga.⍙CallRL                                 377      26.184714399278164          26.184714399278164         377       377
